    aboutIntro: 'At Vaultique, we understand that a watch is more than just a timepiece—it is a reflection of your style, personality, and ambitions. Whether you seek a statement piece, a reliable everyday watch, or a timepiece built for adventure, we make the search effortless and tailored to you.',
    aboutPersonalized: 'Personalized Recommendations, Designed for You',
    aboutPersonalizedDesc: 'With countless options available, finding the right watch can be overwhelming. That is why we have developed an intelligent recommendation system that refines your shopping experience to match your preferences.',
