    faqTitle: 'Vaultique | FAQ',
    faqHeader: 'Frequently Asked Questions',
    faqQ1: 'How do I place an order?',
    faqA1: 'To place an order, simply browse our collection, select your desired watch, customize it if desired, and click "Add to Cart". Follow the checkout process to complete your purchase.',
    faqQ2: 'What payment methods do you accept?',
    faqA2: 'We accept all major credit cards (Visa, MasterCard, American Express), PayPal, and bank transfers. All payments are processed securely through our encrypted payment system.',
    faqQ3: 'Is my payment information secure?',
    faqA3: 'Absolutely. We use industry-standard SSL encryption to protect your payment information. We never store your full credit card details on our servers.',
    faqQ4: 'Do you offer installment plans?',
    faqA4: 'Yes, we offer flexible installment plans through our financing partners. At checkout, you can select the installment option and choose a payment plan that suits your budget.',
    faqQ5: 'How long does shipping take?',
    faqA5: 'Standard shipping typically takes 3-5 business days within the continental US. International shipping may take 7-14 business days depending on the destination.',
    faqQ6: 'Do you ship internationally?',
    faqA6: 'Yes, we ship to most countries worldwide. International shipping rates and delivery times vary by location. You can view shipping options during checkout.',
    faqQ7: 'Is shipping insured?',
    faqA7: 'All shipments are fully insured against loss or damage during transit. You can shop with confidence knowing your purchase is protected from our facility to your doorstep.',
    faqQ8: 'Can I track my order?',
    faqA8: 'Yes, once your order ships, you\'ll receive a tracking number via email. You can use this number on our website or the carrier\'s website to monitor your package\'s journey.',
    faqQ9: 'What is your warranty policy?',
    faqA9: 'All our watches come with a 5-year international warranty covering manufacturing defects. The warranty does not cover damage from accidents, misuse, or normal wear and tear.',
    faqQ10: 'Do your watches come with a warranty?',
    faqA10: 'Yes, every Vaultique watch comes with our comprehensive 5-year warranty. We also offer extended warranty options for collectors and enthusiasts.',
    faqQ11: 'How do I service my watch?',
    faqA11: 'We recommend professional servicing every 3-5 years. You can schedule service through our website, or visit one of our authorized service centers worldwide.',
    faqQ12: 'What if my watch needs repair?',
    faqA12: 'Contact our customer service team to initiate a repair request. Most repairs are completed within 2-4 weeks and covered under warranty if applicable.',
    faqQ13: 'What is your return policy?',
    faqA13: 'We offer a 30-day return policy for all unworn watches in their original condition. Customized watches are not eligible for returns unless they arrive damaged or defective.',
    faqQ14: 'How do I initiate a return?',
    faqA14: 'To initiate a return, contact our customer service team within 30 days of delivery. Include your order number and reason for return. We\'ll provide you with return shipping instructions.',
    faqQ15: 'How long do refunds take to process?',
    faqA15: 'Once we receive your return, refunds are processed within 3-5 business days. It may take an additional 5-10 business days for the refund to appear on your original payment method.',
    faqQ16: 'Do I have to pay return shipping?',
    faqA16: 'For returns due to our error or defective products, we cover return shipping. For other returns, customers are responsible for return shipping costs.',
